OL,3,CPaddleboard firm owner jailed for 10
OL,4,Cyears over fatal tour which killed four
OL,6,FA former police officer who ran a
OL,7,Fpaddleboarding company has been jailed
OL,8,Ffor 10 years and six months after four
OL,9,Fpeople drowned during an excursion on
OL,10,Fa river in Pembrokeshire.
OL,12,FNerys Bethan Lloyd organised a stand-
OL,13,Fup paddleboarding tour on the River
OL,14,FCleddau in Haverfordwest in October
OL,15,F2021 despite "extremely hazardous
OL,16,Fconditions" and weather warnings in
OL,17,Fplace.
OL,19,FLloyd failed to warn the group about a
OL,20,Fweir on the route or how to navigate
OL,21,Fit.
