OL,4,Cyears over fatal tour which killed four
OL,6,FThe participants were swept over, with
OL,7,Fsome becoming trapped under the fast-
OL,8,Fmoving water.
OL,10,FPaul O'Dwyer, 42, Andrea Powell, 41,
OL,11,FMorgan Rogers, 24, and Nicola
OL,12,FWheatley, 40, all died.
OL,14,FLloyd, 39, from Aberavon, south Wales,
OL,15,Fwas the owner and sole director of
OL,16,FSalty Dog Co Ltd, which organised the
OL,17,Ftour.
