OL,6,FShe pleaded guilty to four counts of
OL,7,Fgross negligence manslaughter and one
OL,8,Foffence under the Health and Safety at
OL,9,FWork Act in March, and was sentenced
OL,10,Fby Mrs Justice Dame Mary Stacey at
OL,11,FSwansea Crown Court on Wednesday.
OL,13,FLloyd, a former firearms officer for
OL,14,FSouth Wales Police, appeared in the
OL,15,Fdock wearing a white shirt and dark
OL,16,Ftrousers.
OL,18,FShe stared straight ahead at the judge
OL,19,Fas her sentence was read out.
