OL,6,F"No consent forms were obtained. There
OL,7,Fhad been no mention to the group of a
OL,8,Fweir on the river and how to deal with
OL,9,Fit and no discussion of the tidal
OL,10,Friver conditions whatsoever."
OL,12,FThe judge said there were Met Office
OL,13,Fweather warnings at that time, as well
OL,14,Fas a flood alert in place through
OL,15,FNatural Resources Wales.
OL,17,FShe told Lloyd that she had watched
OL,18,FCCTV footage of the incident, which
OL,19,Fshe described as "too distressing" to
OL,20,Fplay in court.
