OL,13,Fthe aftermath of the incident.
OL,15,FShe also rejected the suggestion that
OL,16,Fthe plan had been to go around the
OL,17,Fweir.
OL,19,F"It is clear to me that you intended
OL,20,Ffor the group to go through the weir,"
