OL,3,CPaddleboard firm owner jailed for 10
OL,4,Cyears over fatal tour which killed four
OL,6,F"Paul (O'Dwyer) had researched
OL,7,Falternative routes that would avoid
OL,8,Fcrossing the weir, all of which were
OL,9,Fdismissed by you.
OL,11,F"He raised valid concerns that you
OL,12,Fignored. Your interest appeared to be
OL,13,Fmore of an exciting route rather than
OL,14,Fsafety."
OL,16,FThe judge accused Lloyd of being "lax"
OL,17,Fwhen it came to health and safety,
OL,18,Fdespite her training as a police
OL,19,Fofficer and as a volunteer for the
OL,20,FRNLI.
