OL,6,FHanding Lloyd a 10-year and six-month
OL,7,Fsentence, the judge told Lloyd: "I
OL,8,Faccept you are desperately sorry for
OL,9,Fwhat happened that day.
OL,11,F"Your life has also been massively
OL,12,Fimpacted. But being sorry for what
OL,13,Fhappened is different from remorse."
OL,15,FLloyd showed no emotion as her
OL,16,Fsentence was read out, only nodding at
OL,17,Fthe judge and mouthing "thank you".
