OL,6,F"Anyone that has lost a child by
OL,7,Fsomeone else's doing will know that
OL,8,Fthere is no pain like it. That day I
OL,9,Flost a piece of myself, I will never
OL,10,Fbe the same person without my Morgan."
OL,12,FMs Hall said that Lloyd's failure to
OL,13,Fget next of kin details meant it was
OL,14,Fmore than 12 hours before she was
OL,15,Finformed of her daughter's death.
OL,17,F"Even then, it was another 12 hours
OL,18,Fbefore I formally identified her
