OL,6,FLisa Rose, specialist prosecutor with
OL,7,Fthe Crown Prosecution Service special
OL,8,Fcrime division, said: "Nerys Lloyd
OL,9,Fshould not have taken participants on
OL,10,Fthe water that day; the heavy flooding
OL,11,Fhad left the river running very fast
OL,12,Fand it was beyond the remit of a
OL,13,Fbeginner's tour.
OL,15,F"The weir itself was in an extremely
OL,16,Fhazardous condition, with a high
OL,17,Fpotential for loss of life, and all
OL,18,Fthe possible exit points nearby had
OL,19,Fbeen flooded out.
